description: A state TV exit poll shows victory for President Alexander Lukashenko - but the opposition cries foul.
title: Belarus election: Clashes after poll predicts Lukashenko re-election
title_page: Belarus election: Clashes after poll predicts Lukashenko re-election - BBC News
maintext: In the last vote in 2015, he was declared winner with 83.5% of the vote. There were no serious challengers and election observers reported problems in the counting and tabulation of votes.
